author: HBO Max
description:
Celebrate Batman Day with Episode 121 of DC Studios Showcase! Frankey Smith, Tyler Coates, and Coy Jandreau debate their favorite Batman and Bruce Wayne portrayals in film, from Michael Keaton to Robert Pattinson. Plus, an exclusive interview with Troy Baker - voice of Batman and The Joker - sharing insights on playing these iconic roles. We also break down Peacemaker Season 2 Episodes 3 & 4, exploring Chris’s different relationships, Economos’s big moments, and what’s next for the DC Universe. Don’t miss this episode packed with Batman lore, Peacemaker analysis, and behind-the-scenes DC stories! 

Troy Baker - Voice Actor @officialtroybaker 
Voice of Joel in The Last of Us (Game & HBO series) 
Voice of Batman in multiple DC Animated projects 
Voice of The Joker in Batman: Arkham Origins 
Voice of Indiana Jones in Indiana Jones and the Great Circle 
Voice roles in Uncharted 4 and Bioshock Infinite 

#BatmanDay #Batman #BruceWayne #TroyBaker #Peacemaker #PeacemakerSeason2 #DCStudios #D

author: HBO Max
description:
Join James Gunn with co-hosts Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt), Steve Agee (John Economos) and special guest Tim Meadows (Langston Fleury) for the latest episode of Peacemaker: The Official Podcast. The team explores Season 2, Episode 4, "Need I Say Door" where Tim discusses the nuances of his role as Langston Fleury while the crew expound on Peacemaker’s existential crisis, the “good us” theme, and Harcourt and Economos’ emotional journey.  

#Peacemaker #JamesGunn #JenniferHolland #SteveAgee #TimMeadows #DCU #HBOMax #PeacemakerPodcast #BehindTheScenes #DCUniverse #LangstonFleury #Season2 #DCEasterEggs
